Context Capital Partners :: Welcome























Firm OverviewContext SummitsContact Us





Delivering Edge
Context Capital Partners is a leading alternative investment specialist firm. Through direct and indirect partnerships Context can provide seed capital, marketing, distribution, operations and infrastructure support to top tier asset managers. Context focus is delivering superior investment solutions to institutional investors and family offices by launching and expanding low correlation investment products that deliver clear edge.


Firm Overview


Context business holdings span asset classes including real estate, specialty finance, hedge funds, and liquid alternatives. To further support the alternative asset ecosystem, Context offers executive recruitment and connects asset managers and investment allocators through a world-class conference business.


Context Capital Partners current business portfolio includes the following:
	
Seed investments in multiple hedge funds and liquid alternative funds
Context | Business Lending – middle market asset based lender
Context | Jensen Partners – executive search for the alternative asset industry
Context Summits – investment conference for the alternative asset industry
Context | Family Network – a global movement to unite affluent families and their executives




Context’s highly experienced in-house team of investment professionals evaluates each fund concept and management team. A rigorous selection process seeks to thoroughly validate business models, market dynamics and operational requirements. Context also pays special attention to the management team’s track record and expertise in the concept area. This vetting process ensures the prospect of high risk-adjusted returns and helps refine the concept for success.
Through a unique approach to identifying, evaluating and overseeing highly differentiated and specialized investment solutions, Context delivers edge as a full financial and operational partner for its fund managers.




About


Context Summits is the efficient frontier for events in the Alternative Asset Management industry. Our mission is to deliver productive, well organized and effective events designed to maximize attendees’ return on investment. Whether you are an asset manager, allocator or service provider, Context Summits will connect you with the experts you need to successfully meet your mandate.
Our next event, Context Summits West, will be held at Monarch Beach Resort, Dana Point, CA on September 17-19, 2017.
Learn more



PRODUCTIVE
Context Summits provides all our participants with the most productive conference environment to conduct business meetings and justify their time and expense.


EFFICIENT
Context Summits understands that our participant's time is valuable. We make the conference experience as efficient as possible with prearranged meetings with participants who have a genuine interest in meeting with one another. The days of roaming the halls and sessions in hopes of meeting someone are over!


FOCUSED
Context Summits are focused on business meetings between managers, investors and industry experts. Meetings are scheduled for the majority of each day with high end networking events in the evening to complete a very productive day for all.





