Context Capital Management



















Our FirmOur Investment TeamOur Investment Philosophy Our Investment StrategiesContact Us


Our Firm
	 

          Context Capital Management, LLC is an SEC-registered alternative asset management firm based in La Jolla, California and Jupiter, Florida.  The firm specializes in fixed income and relative-value strategies with a focus on event-driven credit trades.  Trades are most typically constructed with long convertible and/or corporate bonds and short common stock positions.

	 

          Context’s principals, Michael Rosen and William Fertig have a long and accomplished record in the fixed income space. Our mission is to leverage our insights, experience, and deep network of Wall Street and Industry contacts to generate consistent absolute returns with low correlation to the broad equity and fixed income markets. 

	 

	        





 




